*mhonarc-2.6.16 (19 Oct 2006)

  19 Oct 2006; Ilya A. Volynets-Evenbakh <iluxa@gentoo.org>
  +mhonarc-2.6.16.ebuild:
  Version bump

  07 Oct 2006; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.15.ebuild:
  Making 2.6.15 stable on x86, mips, and sparc. Alpha, amd64, and ppc can
  follow suit when they want, then 2.6.10/11 will get axed. Also adding a fix
  for Bug #123134.

*mhonarc-2.6.15 (29 Dec 2005)

  29 Dec 2005; Stuart Herbert <stuart@gentoo.org> +mhonarc-2.6.15.ebuild:
  Version bump (fixes bug 105356) and fix for sandbox violation (fixes bug 52779)

  28 Nov 2005; <mcumming@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.10.ebuild,
  mhonarc-2.6.11.ebuild:
  Switched from perl-module to perl-app eclass

  15 Sep 2005; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.10.ebuild:
  Mark 2.6.10 stable on alpha

*mhonarc-2.6.10 (28 May 2005)

  28 May 2005; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.10.ebuild,
  +mhonarc-2.6.11.ebuild, -mhonarc-2.6.8-r1.ebuild:
  Version bump and fix to SRC_URI to download the source properly. Removed older
  2.6.8 version. Closes bugs #94074 and #93929.

  21 Aug 2004; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> :
  (long overdue) Revision bump.

*mhonarc-2.6.8-r1 (25 Apr 2004)

  25 Apr 2004; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> +mhonarc-2.6.8-r1.ebuild,
  -mhonarc-2.6.8.ebuild:
  Removed the ugly sedfu lines from src_install, as perl-module_src_install()
  from the perl-module eclass does this now.

*mhonarc-2.6.8 (18 Dec 2003)

  18 Dec 2003; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.8.ebuild:
  Initial import of MHonArc, the popular perl html-to-mail converter

